Ad [Addendum] Dr. Becker Landscape. Comparable paintings, cf. Lot & Daughters, by Herri met de Bles. Bles: with some distant relationships. 1) Stockholm, NM 4623, acquired 1950 with boat & Arco naturale (Lot & Daughters in a tent). Rockformation and the smoke clouds similar otherwise very different composition); 2) Formerly with Robert Finch: River valley between Rockformations, on the left cave with Lot and Daughters.
